Lucene interface with HBase:
---------------------------
Released under Apache License 2.0 .  See LICENSE.txt for more details.



Indexes columns / column families based on Lucene. 

Originally present as part of Apache HBase project. 

Refactored here, under Apache 2.0 License , as before, to be developed independently.


IndexReaders/IndexWriters on top of HBase:
-----------------------------------------

Similar to the idea of Lucandra project by Jake L, with HBase being the sink for the TF-IDF representations.
